{"tid":2201834,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊潤雄：仍要討論教育界是否做強制病毒檢測","createTime":"2020-09-14T06:16:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T06:30:16.000Z","uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ce33e8277a80aa6cc8eb8393c96714f275bab167","tid":2201834,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T06:16:46.000Z","msg":"全港中小學及幼稚園部分年級本月23日恢復面授課程，教育局局長楊潤雄表示，屆時學校只可上半日課，不希望在校午膳增加感染風險，全部學生將於本月29日復課，仍舊是半日課模式，會視乎疫情發展，決定會否回復全日上課。<br />\n<br />\n全文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549497-20200914.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549497-20200914.htm&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8Pno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=bdabcb01\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549497-20200914.htm&h=a85517c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549497-20200914.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f034fc46687b4c2734812007c5ddd93850a841","tid":2201834,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T06:18:05.000Z","msg":"深喉嚇死班細佬都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c7d070cac764f974f2cd1062e9c87375c0fcb52","tid":2201834,"uid":54800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T06:30:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gLAa66d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgLAa66d.gif&h=a4b06f28&s={SIZ